Creating this group to coordinate and manage all responses for the potential risk of Climate
Change misinfo for Search.
Context:
There has a few public press incidents (Vox, NY Times) this past week about FB's stance on
climate change, and we've been getting direction from org leads to ensure Search is high
quality on this topic.
